OL,3,CMan arrested after suspected hate
OL,4,Ccrime at place of worship
OL,6,FA man, in his 50s, was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of a religiously-motivated
OL,8,Fpublic order offence and criminal
OL,9,Fdamage on Tuesday.
OL,11,FHe was questioned and released on
OL,12,Fbail, with conditions preventing him
OL,13,Ffrom visiting certain areas of
OL,14,FMinehead, police said.
OL,16,FThe incidents took place between 15
OL,17,Fand 18 February, but the following
OL,18,Fdays saw reports to the police that
OL,19,Fother offensive graffiti had appeared
OL,20,Fin the town.
