OL,3,CMan arrested after suspected hate
OL,4,Ccrime at place of worship
OL,6,FExtra police patrols have taken place
OL,7,Fto try and reassure the community.
OL,9,FAnyone with information, CCTV or
OL,10,Fdashcam footage has been asked to
OL,11,Fcontact police online or by calling
OL,12,F101 and quoting reference number
OL,13,F5226045306.
